    "description": "Postman/Newman API test collection for reqres.in, covering Users CRUD, Auth, and Colors endpoints. Companion to the REST Assured + TestNG framework in this repository -- demonstrates quick, collaborative, exploratory API testing with chained requests and inline test scripts.",
